Description: System optimization and utility tool for Lilith Linux
 Tweakers is a high-performance system optimization and utility
 tool for Lilith Linux, providing comprehensive system
 optimization and maintenance tools including CPU/memory/storage
 tuning, system cleaning, backup integration, and benchmarking.